802
00:40:55,600 --> 00:40:56,720
Saya buat pertimbangan dulu.

803
00:40:56,720 --> 00:40:58,600
Itu Kumpulan Wen.

804
00:40:59,110 --> 00:41:01,080
Khabarnya, Timbalan Pengurus Wen

805
00:41:01,080 --> 00:41:02,150
di Kumpulan Wen

