juga lelaki kacak.

807
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:07,040
Ramai lelaki kacak di dunia ni.

808
00:41:07,470 --> 00:41:08,230
Namun,

809
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:11,430
saya hanya ada seorang kawan karib.

810
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:13,230
Yue Er, tak usah risau.

811
00:41:13,230 --> 00:41:15,390
Jika awak ingin putuskan hubungan

812
00:41:15,390 --> 00:41:15,920
dengan He Qiao Yan

813
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,470
sepenuhnya,

814
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:19,080
saya pasti akan memihak kepada awak.

815
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:20,840
Berdasarkan

816
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,760
wajah saya yang lawa
dan kebolehan saya,

817
00:41:23,080 --> 00:41:24,920
saya akan dapat kerja lambat-laun.

818
00:41:25,720 --> 00:41:27,080
Khabarnya, awak dah kirim

819
00:41:27,080 --> 00:41:28,880
beratus-ratus salinan resume.

820
00:41:32,350 --> 00:41:33,470
Makan selagi makanan panas.

821
00:41:37,230 --> 00:41:39,350
Encik He, terima kasih

822
00:41:39,720 --> 00:41:40,510
atas hal Ruo Wei.

823
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,430
Tak boleh, tiada gaya pun.

824
00:41:45,150 --> 00:41:46,510
Terima kasih atas hal Ruo Wei.

825
00:41:53,350 --> 00:41:54,150
Mengapa awak berada di sini?

826
00:41:55,040 --> 00:41:55,760
Encik He, saya...

